Package: qgtools
Type: Package
Title: Generic Tools for Linear (Mixed) Models in Quantitative Genetics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Peter", "Soerensen", 
           email = "first.last@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    A generic model-specification and dispatch layer for linear (mixed) models
    with support for genomic, pedigree, and multi-kernel covariance structures.
    The package decouples statistical model specification from computational
    engines.
